      • DATETIME

        public static final FHIRDefinedTypeEnum DATETIME
        Code Value: dateTime A date, date-time or partial date (e.g. just year or year + month). If hours and minutes are specified, a time zone SHALL be populated. The format is a union of the schema types gYear, gYearMonth, date and dateTime. Seconds may be provided but may also be ignored. Dates SHALL be valid dates.
